nt. Can return: Ordered list containing layoutName:string, numberOfPages:integer, pageWidthInPoints:fixed, pageHeightInPoints:fixed, allPagesAreSameSize:boolean, layoutPolicy:off/scale/recenter/guide based/object based/use master/preserve existing, allPagesUseSamePolicy:boolean, anyPagesWithPolicyOff:boolean."></result></command><command name="get attached devices" code="K2  gadi" description="This will return an array of structs containing information about the attached devices."><parameter name="device type" code="Rpdt" type="adte" description="The type of device to list."></parameter><result type="any" description="An array of structs containing information about the attached devices of the type specified. Can return: Ordered list containing deviceID:string, width:integer, height:integer, ppi:integer, os:string, deviceModel:string, viewerVersion:string, viewerReleaseVersion:string."></result></command><command name="get digpub article version" code="K2  gdAv" description="Get the current digital publishing article version number for the given parameter."><parameter name="digpub article version" code="pdAv" type="dpAt" description="Version string(s) to retrieve."></parameter><result type="text" description="The version string(s) requested."></result></command><command name="get digpub version" code="K2  gdpv" description="Get the current digital publishing version number for the given parameter."><parameter name="digpub version" code="pdpv" type="dpvt" description="Version string(s) to retrieve."></parameter><result type="text" description="The version string(s) requested."></result></command><command name="get documents ids" code="K2  sgdi" description="Gets the instance ids of all open documents."><result type="text" description="The XML string representing the documents ids."></result></command><command name="get supported article viewer versions" code="K2  gVAs" description="Get the list of article viewer versions the digital publishing plugin supports."><resu