r the object."></property><property name="overprint fill" code="ovpr" type="boolean" description="If true, the WMF's fill color overprints any underlying objects. If false, the fill color knocks out the underlying colors."></property><property name="overprint gap" code="gapO" type="boolean" description="If true, the gap color overprints any underlying colors. If false, the gap color knocks out the underlying colors."></property><property name="overprint stroke" code="sovp" type="boolean" description="If true, the WMF's stroke color overprints any underlying objects. If false, the stroke color knocks out the  underlying colors."></property><property name="overridden" code="Ovrn" type="boolean" access="r" description="If true, the object originated on a master spread and was overridden. If false, the object either originated on a master spread and was not overridden, or the object did not originate on a master page."></property><property name="overridden master page item" code="ovrp" type="specifier" access="r" description="An object that originated on a master page and has been overridden. Can return: page item, guide, graphic, movie or sound."></property><property name="parent" code="pare" type="specifier" access="r" description="The parent of the WMF (a spline item, polygon, graphic line, rectangle, oval, state, text box, signature field, combo box, list box, XML element, place gun or snippet). Can return: spline item, polygon, graphic line, rectangle, oval, state, text box, signature field, combo box, list box, XML element, place gun or snippet."></property><property name="parent page" code="PaPa" type="page" access="r" description="The page on which this page item appears."></property><property name="properties" code="qpro" type="record" description="A property that allows setting of several properties at the same time."></property><property name="right arrow head scale" code="rahs" type="real" description="The scaling applied to the arrowhead at the end of the p