on/right to left direction or nothing."></property><property name="paragraph gyoudori" code="jpgd" type="any" description="If true, the gyoudori mode applies to the entire paragraph. If false, the gyoudori mode applies to each line in the paragraph. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="paragraph justification" code="pjus" type="any" description="Paragraph justification. Can return: default justification/arabic justification/naskh justification/naskh tatweel justification/naskh kashida justification/naskh tatweel justification frac/naskh kashida justification frac or nothing."></property><property name="paragraph kashida width" code="pkas" type="any" description="Paragraph kashida width. 0 is none, 1 is short, 2 is medium, 3 is long. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="parent" code="pare" type="specifier" access="r" description="The parent of the change text preference (a application)."></property><property name="point size" code="ptsz" type="any" description="The text size. Can return: number or string or nothing."></property><property name="position" code="posm" type="any" description="The text position relative to the baseline. Can return: normal/superscript/subscript/OT superscript/OT subscript/OT numerator/OT denominator or nothing."></property><property name="positional form" code="OTPf" type="any" description="The OpenType positional form. Can return: none/calculate/initial/medial/final/isolated or nothing."></property><property name="properties" code="qpro" type="record" description="A property that allows setting of several properties at the same time."></property><property name="rensuuji" code="jren" type="any" description="If true, disallows line breaks in numbers. If false, lines can break between digits in multi-digit numbers. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="right indent" code="inbr" type="any" description="The width of the right indent. Can return: number or string or nothing."></property><property name="rotate single byte characters" code="jro1" type="any" description="If true, rotates Roman characters in vertical text. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="ruby alignment" code="jral" type="any" description="The ruby alignment. Can return: ruby left/ruby center/ruby right/ruby full justify/ruby JIS/ruby equal aki/ruby 1 aki or nothing."></property><property name="ruby auto align" code="jraa" type="any" description="If true, auto aligns ruby. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="ruby auto scaling" code="jras" type="any" description="If true, automatically scales ruby to the specified percent of parent text size. For information on specifying a percent, see ruby parent scaling percent. . Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="ruby auto tcy auto scale" code="jrts" type="any" description="If true, automatically scales glyphs in auto tcy (tate-chuu-yoko) in ruby to fit one em. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="ruby auto tcy digits" code="jrtd" type="any" description="The number of digits included in auto tcy (tate-chuu-yoko) in ruby. Can return: small integer or nothing."></property><property name="ruby auto tcy include roman" code="jrtr" type="any" description="If true, includes Roman characters in auto tcy (tate-chuu-yoko) in ruby. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="ruby fill" code="jrfl" type="any" description="The swatch (color, gradient, tint, or mixed ink) applied to the fill of ruby characters. Can return: swatch, string or nothing."></property><property name="ruby font" code="jrfn" type="any" description="The font applied to ruby characters. Can return: font, string or nothing."></property><property name="ruby font size" code="jrfs" type="any" description="The size (in points) of ruby characters. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="ruby font style" code="jrft" type="any" description="The font style of ruby characters. Can return: string or nothing."></property><property name="ruby open type pro" code="jpro" type="any" description="If true, uses OpenType Pro fonts for ruby. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="ruby overhang" code="jrov" type="any" description="If true, constrains ruby overhang to the specified amount. For information on specifying an amount, see ruby parent overhang amount. . Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="ruby overprint fill" code="jrof" type="any" description="The method of overprinting the ruby fill. Can return: auto/overprint on/overprint off or nothing."></property><property name="ruby overprint stroke" code="jros" type="any" description="The method of overprinting the ruby stroke. Can return: auto/overprint on/overprint off or nothing."></property><property name="ruby parent overhang amount" code="jrva" type="any" description="The amount by which ruby characters can overhang the parent text. Can return: none/ruby overhang one ruby/ruby overhang half ruby/ruby overhang one char/ruby overhang half char/ruby overhang no limit or nothing."></property><property name="ruby parent scaling percent" code="jrsc" type="any" description="The amount (as a percentage) to scale the parent text size to determine the ruby text size. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="ruby parent spacing" code="jrsp" type="any" description="The ruby spacing relative to the parent text. . Can return: ruby parent no adjustment/ruby parent both sides/ruby parent 121 aki/ruby parent equal aki/ruby parent full justify or nothing."></property><property name="ruby position" code="jrpz" type="any" description="The position of ruby characters relative to the parent text. Can return: above right/below left or nothing."></property><property name="ruby stroke" code="jrsk" type="any" description="The swatch (color, gradient, tint, or mixed ink) applied to the stroke of ruby characters. Can return: swatch, string or nothing."></property><property name="ruby stroke tint" code="jrst" type="any" description="The stroke tint (as a percentage) of ruby characters. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="ruby tint" code="jrti" type="any" description="The tint (as a percentage) of the ruby fill color. (Range: 0 to 100). Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="ruby type" code="jrtp" type="any" description="The ruby type. Can return: group ruby/per character ruby or nothing."></property><property name="ruby weight" code="jrwt" type="any" description="The stroke weight (in points) of ruby characters. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="ruby X offset" code="jrxo" type="any" description="The amount of horizontal space between ruby and parent characters. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="ruby X scale" code="jrwd" type="any" description="The horizontal size of ruby characters, specified as a percent of the original size. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="ruby Y offset" code="jryo" type="any" description="The amount of vertical space between ruby and parent characters. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="ruby Y scale" code="jrpt" type="any" description="The vertical size of ruby characters, specified as a percent of the original size. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="same para style spacing" code="spsp" type="any" description="The space between paragraphs using same style. Can return: number or string, SetIgnore or nothing."></property><property name="scale affects line height" code="jslh" type="any" description="If true, the line changes size when characters are scaled. . Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="shatai adjust rotation" code="jshr" type="any" description="If true, applies shatai rotation. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="shatai adjust tsume" code="jsht" type="any" description="If 