eturn: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="ruby auto tcy auto scale" code="jrts" type="any" description="If true, automatically scales glyphs in auto tcy (tate-chuu-yoko) in ruby to fit one em. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="ruby auto tcy digits" code="jrtd" type="any" description="The number of digits included in auto tcy (tate-chuu-yoko) in ruby. Can return: small integer or nothing."></property><property name="ruby auto tcy include roman" code="jrtr" type="any" description="If true, includes Roman characters in auto tcy (tate-chuu-yoko) in ruby. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="ruby fill" code="jrfl" type="any" description="The swatch (color, gradient, tint, or mixed ink) applied to the fill of ruby characters. Can return: swatch, string or nothing."></property><property name="ruby font" code="jrfn" type="any" description="The font applied to ruby characters. Can return: font, string or nothing."></property><property name="ruby font size" code="jrfs" type="any" description="The size (in points) of ruby characters. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="ruby font style" code="jrft" type="any" description="The font style of ruby characters. Can return: string or nothing."></property><property name="ruby open type pro" code="jpro" type="any" description="If true, uses OpenType Pro fonts for ruby. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="ruby overhang" code="jrov" type="any" description="If true, constrains ruby overhang to the specified amount. For information on specifying an amount, see ruby parent overhang amount. . Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="ruby overprint fill" code="jrof" type="any" description="The method of overprinting the ruby fill. Can return: auto/overprint on/overprint off or nothing."></property><property name="ruby overprint stroke" code="jros" type="any" description="The method of overprinting the ruby stroke. Can return: auto/overprint on/overprint off or nothing."></property><property name="ruby parent overhang amount" code="jrva" type="any" description="The amount by which ruby characters can overhang the parent text. Can return: none/ruby overhang one ruby/ruby overhang half ruby/ruby overhang one char/ruby overhang half char/ruby overhang no limit or nothing."></property><property name="ruby parent scaling percent" code="jrsc" type="any" description="The amount (as a percentage) to scale the parent text size to determine the ruby text size. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="ruby parent spacing" code="jrsp" type="any" description="The ruby spacing relative to the parent text. . Can return: ruby parent no adjustment/ruby parent both sides/ruby parent 121 aki/ruby parent equal aki/ruby parent full justify or nothing."></property><property name="ruby position" code="jrpz" type="any" description="The position of ruby characters relative to the parent text. Can return: above right/below left or nothing."></property><property name="ruby stroke" code="jrsk" type="any" description="The swatch (color, gradient, tint, or mixed ink) applied to the stroke of ruby characters. Can return: swatch, string or nothing."></property><property name="ruby stroke tint" code="jrst" type="any" description="The stroke tint (as a percentage) of ruby characters. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="ruby tint" code="jrti" type="any" description="The tint (as a percentage) of the ruby fill color. (Range: 0 to 100). Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="ruby type" code="jrtp" type="any" description="The ruby type. Can return: group ruby/per character ruby or nothing."></property><property name="ruby weight" code="jrwt" type="any" description="The stroke weight (in points) of ruby characters. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="ruby X offset" code="jrxo" type="any" description="The amount of horizontal space between ruby and parent characters. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="ruby X scale" code="jrwd" type="any" description="The horizontal size of ruby characters, specified as a percent of the original size. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="ruby Y offset" code="jryo" type="any" description="The amount of vertical space between ruby and parent characters. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="ruby Y scale" code="jrpt" type="any" description="The vertical size of ruby characters, specified as a percent of the original size. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="scale affects line height" code="jslh" type="any" description="If true, the line changes size when characters are scaled. . Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="shatai adjust rotation" code="jshr" type="any" description="If true, applies shatai rotation. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="shatai adjust tsume" code="jsht" type="any" description="If true, adjusts shatai tsume. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="shatai degree angle" code="jsha" type="any" description="The shatai lens angle (in degrees). Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="shatai magnification" code="jshp" type="any" description="The amount (as a percentage) of shatai obliquing to apply. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="skew" code="pskw" type="any" description="The skew angle of the character style. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="split document" code="exbr" type="any" description="Split Document (EPUB only). Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="strike through color" code="stco" type="any" description="The swatch (color, gradient, tint, or mixed ink) applied to the strikethrough stroke. Can return: swatch, string or nothing."></property><property name="strike through gap color" code="stgc" type="any" description="The swatch (color, gradient, tint, or mixed ink) applied to the gap of the strikethrough stroke. Can return: swatch, string or nothing."></property><property name="strike through gap overprint" code="stgo" type="any" description="If true, the gap color of the strikethrough stroke will overprint. Note: Valid when strike through type is not solid. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="strike through gap tint" code="stgt" type="any" description="The tint (as a percentage) of the strikethrough stroke gap color. (Range: 0 to 100) Note: Valid when strike through type is not solid. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="strike through offset" code="stos" type="any" description="The amount by which to offset the strikethrough stroke from the text baseline. Can return: number or string or nothing."></property><property name="strike through overprint" code="Stvp" type="any" description="If true, the strikethrough stroke will overprint. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="strike through tint" code="sttt" type="any" description="The tint (as a percentage) of the strikethrough stroke. (Range: 0 to 100). Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="strike through type" code="sttp" type="any" description="The stroke type of the strikethrough stroke. Can return: stroke style, string or nothing."></property><property name="strike through weight" code="stwt" type="any" description="The stroke weight of the strikethrough stroke. Can return: number or string or nothing."></property><property name="strike thru" code="strk" type="any" description="If true, draws a strikethrough line through the text. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="stroke alignment" code="strA" type="any" description="The stroke alignment applied to the text. Can return: center alignment/outside alignment or nothing."></property><property name="stroke color" code="lncl" type="any" description="The swatch (color, gradient, tint, or mixed ink) applied to the stroke of the character style. Can return: swatch or nothing. Can also accept: string."></property><property name="stroke tint" code="lint" type="any" description="The tint (as a percentage) of the stroke color of the character style. (To specify a tint percentage, use a number in the range of 0 to 100; to use the inherited or overridden value, use -1.). Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="stroke weight" code="lnwt" type="any" description="The stroke weight applied to the characters of the text. Can return: number or string or nothing."></property><property name="tatechuyoko" code="jtcy" type="any" description="If true, makes the character horizontal in vertical text. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="tatechuyoko X offset" code="jtax" type="any" description="The horizontal offset for horizontal characters in vertical text. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="tatechuyoko Y offset" code="jtay" type="any" description="The vertical offset for horizontal characters in vertical text. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="tracking" code="trak" type="any" description="The amount by which to loosen or tighten a block of text, specified in thousands of an em. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="trailing aki" code="jmas" type="any" description="The amount of space after each character. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="tsume" code="tsum" type="any" description="The amount of horizontal character compression. Can return: fixed or nothing."></property><property name="underline" code="undr" type="any" description="If true, underlines the text. Can return: boolean or nothing."></property><property name="underline color" code="ulco" type="any" description="The swatch (color, gradient, tint, or mixed ink) applied to the underline stroke. . Can return: swatch, string or nothing."></property><property n