dth, and right margin constraints this item is subject to when using the object-based layout rule."><type type="LPdc" list="yes"></type></property><property name="horizontal scale" code="phzs" type="real" description="The horizontal scaling applied to the endnote text frame."></property><property name="id" code="ID  " type="integer" access="r" description="The unique ID of the endnote text frame."></property><property name="index" code="pidx" type="integer" access="r" description="The index of the endnote text frame within its containing object."></property><property name="item layer" code="pilr" type="layer" description="The layer that the endnote text frame is on."></property><property name="label" code="ptag" type="text" description="A property that can be set to any string."></property><property name="left arrow head scale" code="lahs" type="real" description="The scaling applied to the arrowhead at the start of the path. (Range: 1 to 1000)"></property><property name="left line end" code="llen" type="ahed" description="The arrowhead applied to the start of the path. "></property><property name="linked Page Item options" code="lpip" type="linked Page Item option" access="r" description="Linked Page Item options"></property><property name="local display setting" code="pLDs" type="dsps" description="Display performance options for the endnote text frame."></property><property name="locked" code="plck" type="boolean" description="If true, the endnote text frame is locked."></property><property name="miter limit" code="mitr" type="real" description="The limit of the ratio of stroke width to miter length before a miter (pointed) join becomes a bevel (squared-off) join. Can return: fixed (1 - 500)."></property><property name="name" code="pnam" type="text" description="The name of the endnote text frame."></property><property name="next text frame" code="ntxf" type="specifier" description="The next text frame in the thread. Can return: text frame or text path. Can also 