rue, the gyoudori mode applies to the entire paragraph. If false, the gyoudori mode applies to each line in the paragraph."></property><property name="paragraph justification" code="pjus" type="pjut" description="Paragraph justification."></property><property name="paragraph kashida width" code="pkas" type="real" description="Paragraph kashida width. 0 is none, 1 is short, 2 is medium, 3 is long"></property><property name="paragraph shading bottom  right corner option" code="scO4" type="coPt" description="The shape to apply to the bottom right corner of rectangular shapes."></property><property name="paragraph shading bottom left corner option" code="scO3" type="coPt" description="The shape to apply to the bottom left corner of rectangular shapes."></property><property name="paragraph shading bottom left corner radius" code="scr3" description="The radius in measurement units of the corner effect applied to the bottom left corner of rectangular shapes"><type type="number"></type><type type="text"></type></property><property name="paragraph shading bottom offset" code="psOb" description="The distance to offset the bottom edge of the paragraph."><type type="number"></type><type type="text"></type></property><property name="paragraph shading bottom origin" code="psBo" type="psBe" description="The basis (descent or baseline) used to calculate the bottom origin of the paragraph shading."></property><property name="paragraph shading bottom right corner radius" code="scr4" description="The radius in measurement units of the corner effect applied to the bottom right corner of rectangular shapes"><type type="number"></type><type type="text"></type></property><property name="paragraph shading clip to frame" code="psCf" type="boolean" description="If true, forces the shading of the paragraph to be clipped with respect to frame shape."></property><property name="paragraph shading color" code="psFc" type="any" description="The swatch (color, gradient, tint, or mixed ink) applied 