ke of the characters will overprint."></property><property name="paragraph border bottom  right corner option" code="bcO4" type="coPt" description="The shape to apply to the bottom right corner of rectangular shapes."></property><property name="paragraph border bottom left corner option" code="bcO3" type="coPt" description="The shape to apply to the bottom left corner of rectangular shapes."></property><property name="paragraph border bottom left corner radius" code="bcr3" description="The radius in measurement units of the corner effect applied to the bottom left corner of rectangular shapes"><type type="number"></type><type type="text"></type></property><property name="paragraph border bottom line weight" code="psWB" description="The bottom line weight of the border of paragraph."><type type="number"></type><type type="text"></type></property><property name="paragraph border bottom offset" code="pbOb" description="The distance to offset the bottom edge of the paragraph border."><type type="number"></type><type type="text"></type></property><property name="paragraph border bottom origin" code="pbBo" type="pbBe" description="The basis (descent or baseline) used to calculate the bottom origin of the paragraph border."></property><property name="paragraph border bottom right corner radius" code="bcr4" description="The radius in measurement units of the corner effect applied to the bottom right corner of rectangular shapes"><type type="number"></type><type type="text"></type></property><property name="paragraph border color" code="psSc" type="any" description="The swatch (color, gradient, tint, or mixed ink) applied to the paragraph stroke. Can return: swatch or string."></property><property name="paragraph border display if splits" code="pbDf" type="boolean" description="If true, then paragraph border is also displayed at the points where the paragraph splits across frames or columns."></property><property name="paragraph border gap color" code="psGc" type="any" descr